{"tid":2234763,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"造神堪比毛澤東 與馬列平起平坐  清華大學必修「習思想」","createTime":"2020-10-08T06:30:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-09T07:03:32.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"a47a91b787d5d52e9c06185750be79833667ac6b","tid":2234763,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T06:30:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201008/E4SJXKV225HNNFYCP26EO7MBSQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201008%2FE4SJXKV225HNNFYCP26EO7MBSQ%2F&d=xM4HlgsByf6UCiwKp%2FWW5IaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=9565264d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201008%2FE4SJXKV225HNNFYCP26EO7MBSQ%2F&h=fb5b5e4d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201008/E4SJXKV225HNNFYCP26EO7MBSQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n造神堪比毛澤東 與馬列平起平坐 <br />\n清華大學必修「習思想」<br />\n<br />\n【個人崇拜】內地不少大學已經開學近一個月，黨媒早前指新學期至少37所高等院校將全面開設「習近平新時代中國特色社會主義思想概論」課， 有傳媒就發現不少院校開辦課程外，更將「習近平思想」設為必修課，當中包括清華大學。時事評論員對本報分析指，習近平已經全面把自己的地位提升到與馬克思、列寧、毛澤東等平起平坐，造神的程度與毛時代已不相伯仲。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：戰狼外交 武肺肆虐  歐亞民眾負評中國<br />\n<br />\n內地高等學府素有「馬原」、「毛概」、「思修」等思政必修科課程，即《馬克思主義基本原理概論》、《毛澤東思想和中國特色社會主義理論體系概論》和《思想道德修養與法律基礎》。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/jeZitAEIF1txFrBcs--1PvITywc=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7HLJ444AWRHRBBO5OJF46JAHTA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FjeZitAEIF1txFrBcs--1PvITywc%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7HLJ444AWRHRBBO5OJF46JAHTA.jpg&h=281fa332&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■習思想的箝制將深入中國各大名校。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全國37所高等院校開班<br />\n<br />\n當中清華大學的經管學院本科生除了需要修習「馬原」、。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n另據本報查找內地多所大學網站，它們對「習近平思想」這一科都十分重視。山東大學也與清華大學一樣，「習近平思想」為必修課程，納入畢業要求，。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n而北京大學的「習近平思想」課就分成三學分和兩學分兩科；華東師範大學分有多個教研部，有兩個是馬克思主義的教研部，一個是習近平思想的教研部；上海技術工程大學上周二（9月29日）更召開會議，要老師集體就着「習近平思想」開會備課，嚴陣以待。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/viax7871wElaX6iDfiqswTKy-1I=/1770x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RXPV5RRSHRBEDC73C25AQPA5CU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fviax7871wElaX6iDfiqswTKy-1I%3D%2F1770x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRXPV5RRSHRBEDC73C25AQPA5CU.jpg&h=871f2d8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■內地街頭隨處可見宣傳習近平思想。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n老師開會備課 嚴陣以待<br />\n<br />\n去年中共中央辦公廳、國務院辦公廳印發了《關於深化新時代學校思想政治理論課改革創新的若干意見》，已表明要改善思政課課程教材體系，及加強以「習近平思想」為核心內容的思政課課程。時事評論員林和立對本報指，這類型習近平思想研究以前都是停留在校內的研究中心，但過去一年習近平思想研究的深度和寬度都變得更厲害，不單走出校園，由外交部成立習近平思想研究中心，更把「習近平思想」定為必修科，這種製造偶像崇拜，在程度上與毛澤東時代已經相差無幾。<br />\n<br />\n另外，林和立指，習近平思想在過去一年不斷出現在各級、各類型的會議，可說是無孔不入，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n自由亞洲電台／《蘋果》記者<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/p0lNacFY6FnZitMLyp5Aeo-lVIU=/1682x2559/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LEUA466OQVBDPIKVMA7OLKHB6Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fp0lNacFY6FnZitMLyp5Aeo-lVIU%3D%2F1682x2559%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLEUA466OQVBDPIKVMA7OLKHB6Q.jpg&h=a579f7b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■奉行極左路線的習近平十分看重意識形態。"},{"pid":"f163859c9b0913eba8f492daf62aa10198dae32d","tid":2234763,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T06:35:40.000Z","msg":"可以研究當代最偉大的習近平思想 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://assets.post852.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/03173744/image1504431388263.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.post852.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F09%2F03173744%2Fimage1504431388263.png&h=dff5d13b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://assets.post852.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/26204555/image1530016948976.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.post852.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F26204555%2Fimage1530016948976.png&h=99aa5912&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b842d992e2099fab4032a325a2c7c54d5679f022","tid":2234763,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T06:36:31.000Z","msg":"小學生有咩資格 <img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/throw.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cb35cb5172e7da1827687b8e6a7ef3354a45ed1","tid":2234763,"uid":300006,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T06:37:41.000Z","msg":"真係唔知佢有咩做過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6df9206f1b577d73b2e147841178e5a5b91c70b8","tid":2234763,"uid":143499,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T06:38:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0ee392bb2351d86f49470209524ebcb4b17abaf2","tid":2234763,"uid":272652,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T06:38:16.000Z","msg":"真心想買本黎睇下"},{"pid":"117ef0d9d59b65c9e78693b9c20e6c918d586c4d","tid":2234763,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T06:38:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"013353f8b9c82dd48fea72227deda1f32ac07802","tid":2234763,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"117ef0d9d59b65c9e78693b9c20e6c918d586c4d","tid":2234763,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4cb35cb5172e7da1827687b8e6a7ef3354a45ed1","tid":2234763,"uid":300006,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T06:37:41.000Z","msg":"真係唔知佢有咩做過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T06:38:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T06:39:21.000Z","msg":"<spa