TA.jpg&h=281fa332&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■習思想的箝制將深入中國各大名校。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全國37所高等院校開班<br />\n<br />\n當中清華大學的經管學院本科生除了需要修習「馬原」、。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n另據本報查找內地多所大學網站，它們對「習近平思想」這一科都十分重視。山東大學也與清華大學一樣，「習近平思想」為必修課程，納入畢業要求，。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n而北京大學的「習近平思想」課就分成三學分和兩學分兩科；華東師範大學分有多個教研部，有兩個是馬克思主義的教研部，一個是習近平思想的教研部；上海技術工程大學上周二（9月29日）更召開會議，要老師集體就着「習近平思想」開會備課，嚴陣以待。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/viax7871wElaX6iDfiqswTKy-1I=/1770x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RXPV5RRSHRBEDC73C25AQPA5CU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fviax7871wElaX6iDfiqswTKy-1I%3D%2F1770x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRXPV5RRSHRBEDC73C25AQPA5CU.jpg&h=871f2d8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■內地街頭隨處可見宣傳習近平思想。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n老師開會備課 嚴陣以待<br />\n<br />\n去年中共中央辦公廳、國務院辦公廳印發了《關於深化新時代學校思想政治理論課改革創新的若干意見》，已表明要改善思政課課程教材體系，及加強以「習近平思想」為核心內容的思政課課程。時事評論員林和立對本報指，這類型習近平思想研究以前都是停留在校內的研究中心，但過去一年習近平思想研究的深度和寬度都變得更厲害，不單走出校園，由外交部成立習近平思想研究中心，更把「習近平思想」定為必修科，這種製造偶像崇拜，在程度上與毛澤東時代已經相差無幾。<br />\n<br />\n另外，林和立指，習近平思想在過去一年不斷出現在各級、各類型的會議，可說是無孔不入，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n自由亞洲電台／《蘋果》記者<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/p0lNacFY6FnZitMLyp5Aeo-lVIU=/1682x2559/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LEUA466OQVBDPIKVMA7OLKHB6Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fp0lNacFY6FnZitMLyp5Aeo-lVIU%3D%2F1682x2559%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLEUA466OQVBDPIKVMA7OLKHB6Q.jpg&h=a579f7b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■奉行極左路線的習近平十分看重意識形態。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T06:54:33.000Z","msg":"「總加速師是狗」。讀完。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"436f007424807afa4802d3d80d69233c91be5cab","tid":2234763,"uid":364850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T06:57:35.000Z","msg":"毛魔： 我太善良<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b790d81e2b2b3f1e3866333821b609db0748c56","tid":2234763,"uid":256019,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T07:00:49.000Z","msg":"上帝要人滅亡，必先令他瘋狂，繼續煲大佢，將佢捧到天咁高係好事，自我澎脹到有日被人屌打，最怕佢而家知驚識縮！所以我最高興係繼續睇到佢地做柒事，愈過份愈好，每做多件柒事，代表加快滅亡速度！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a0fe924dba62591318d4504aa92a02613f3871c","tid":2234763,"uid":24730,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T07:04:13.000Z","msg":"全支那要研究一個小學生嘅思想<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d85c220c40f5c722c7c33ebf49d7a3bf9b0555f3","tid":2234763,"uid":186882,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0ee392bb2351d86f49470209524ebcb4b17abaf2","tid":2234763,"uid":272652,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T06:38:16.000Z","msg":"真心想買本黎睇下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T07:06:02.000Z","msg":"買本翻去做proofreading<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />死好多腦細胞"},{"pid":"77acbb508d13f77939abcb2fa32394f54fdc081e","tid":2234763,"uid":133529,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T07:12:14.000Z","msg":"撚屌平思想一個字概括， 稱帝。<br />\n<br />\n係上帝， 撚屌平說要有光，就有光了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d6b924e6538df4a38ebf371aee57bfb5e551163","tid":2234763,"uid":258345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T07:17:53.000Z","msg":"講撚左咁多年，我都冇聽人解釋過係咩野黎"},{"pid":"2ffd99c230a82c2ceb61ed0221b8a6f4595806bd","tid":2234763,"uid":249794,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T07:21:00.000Z","msg":"聽過好多次究